<h5 data-zesty-id="content:text:1:86"><strong>Headliner&nbsp;- $30,000</strong></h5>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:2:83">
	The Headliner Sponsor receives the highest level of visibility, recognition, and hospitality associated with GameDay Café. This exclusive partnership positions your organization as a lead supporter of The Salvation Army of the Midlands while aligning your brand with one of the region’s most iconic live-music fundraising events.
</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:3:36">
	<strong>Benefits include:</strong>
</p>
<ul data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:4:95">
	<li>Reserved <strong>VIP table seating for up to 10 guests</strong></li>
	<li><strong>Meet &amp; Greet with the artists</strong></li>
	<li>Heavy hors d’oeuvres by Southern Way Catering</li>
	<li>Full bar prior to the show (6:30–8:00 p.m.)</li>
	<li>Wine and beer service at the table during the show</li>
	<li><strong>Top-tier Logo recognition</strong> across all event platforms and locations</li>
	<li>Inclusion in <strong>major network media promotions</strong></li>
	<li>Prominent logo placement on all event promotional materials, including invitations</li>
	<li>Table signage featuring your organization’s logo</li>
	<li>Recognition in all GameDay Café social media event posts</li>
	<li>Logo placement on <strong>The Salvation Army of the Midlands website</strong></li>
	<li>Recognition in <strong>The Salvation Army of the Midlands June newsletter</strong></li>
	<li>Marketing materials displayed at event check-in</li>
	<li><strong>On-stage Recognition </strong>with verbal acknowledgment by the emcee and Major Craddock prior to the show</li>
</ul>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:5:11"></div>
<h5 data-zesty-id="content:text:7:94"><strong>Opening Act - 20,000</strong></h5>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:8:20">
