</p>
<ul data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:9:39">
	<li>Reserved <strong>VIP table seating for up to 10 guests</strong></li>
	<li><strong>Meet &amp; Greet with the artists</strong></li>
	<li>Heavy hors d’oeuvres by Southern Way Catering</li>
	<li>Full bar prior to the show (6:30–8:00 p.m.)</li>
	<li>Wine and beer service at the table during the show</li>
	<li>Logo recognition across all major event platforms</li>
	<li>Inclusion in major network media promotions</li>
	<li>Logo placement on event promotional materials and invitations</li>
	<li>Table signage with organization logo</li>
	<li>Recognition in GameDay Café social media event posts</li>
	<li>Logo placement on The Salvation Army of the Midlands website</li>
	<li>Recognition in the June newsletter</li>
	<li><strong>Verbal recognition</strong> by the emcee and Major Craddock prior to the show</li>
</ul>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:10:23"></div>
<h5 data-zesty-id="content:text:12:1"><strong>Green Room - $15,000</strong></h5>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:13:48">Green Room Sponsors receive a strong balance of hospitality and brand visibility in an intimate, high-energy setting.</p>
<ul data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:14:51">
	<li>Reserved <strong>VIP table seating for up to 8 guests</strong></li>
	<li>Heavy hors d’oeuvres by Southern Way Catering</li>
	<li>Full bar prior to the show (6:30–8:00 p.m.)</li>
	<li>Wine and beer service at the table during the show</li>
